{"tid":592121,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個永世難忘嘅夢境(非ff)","createTime":"2018-03-14T03:35:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T11:16:30.000Z","uid":176311,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d2fb615833b4d5aff11be31525df45d30e1ca4a4","tid":592121,"uid":176311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T03:35:30.000Z","msg":"我好記得嗰晚係10年世界盃決賽，我原本諗住較定鬧鐘起身睇波，點知發夢夢見自己身處大峽谷，見到有個女人唔知做緊乜嘢，行埋去睇下發現佢斬緊男人條撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，然後掉落峽谷下面，我望下下面，見到有如投鞭斷流一樣，全部都係撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，嚇到我即刻醒咗兼鳩縮，飆曬冷汗，然後腳震住行出去睇波"},{"pid":"9d36e2db70d75ea0fe8e2790d16d28a600805d03","tid":592121,"uid":176311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T03:43:35.000Z","msg":"隔咗八年我都重記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2bf4044689a8f36d79a4e09d3acbe5a9777642","tid":592121,"uid":33459,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T03:47:38.000Z","msg":"一插入去隻雞個閪就射咗 跟住佢笑我啦<br />\n我就話再嚟多q 睇下點囉  點知又係秒射<br />\n笑到隻雞無啦啦潮吹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我好尷尬跟手錢都冇畀就落樓<br />\n一開門見到我老母 同佢一齊返屋企 <br />\n成個夢都唔知想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622c0ff5ff49d8d3a20cc9a8d5202774dfe6375c","tid":592121,"uid":176311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T04:11:38.000Z","msg":"重有個係我夢到自己喺未來，啲人係生活喺水入面，平時要游水或者用潛水艇代步"},{"pid":"2c8c069fc0dec2924fac4ca9ac561f8f89bcf113","tid":592121,"uid":176311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T06:10:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4decf3d29c2a8e337463677f4224c12d587def4d","tid":592121,"uid":176311,"like":0,"dislik