好真 醒咗隻眼仲流緊眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c56324c96181925f6c912162346d362481b9a7","tid":592121,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:57:22.000Z","msg":"琴晚<br />\n發夢見到gugudan最細2個成員做左我個妹。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/14/185053_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F14%2F185053_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=183e149d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大妹(<span style=\"color: gold;\">康美娜</span>)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/14/185021_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F14%2F185021_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c22ea196&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二妹(<span style=\"color: gold;\">趙慧妍</span>)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/14/185036_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F14%2F185036_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=96e2dcdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後打仗 我同大妹(<span style=\"color: gold;\">康美娜</span>) 成為第一隊戰鬥人員  正準備出戰  點知轉個撚頭過話解散 <br />\n<br />\n變成全國人都要參戰 要用身份證過大閘(好似香港e道咁 ) 咁我地又出戰 我同兩個妹 仲有見到 我阿嫲 原來阿嫲都係一個戰士<br />\n<br />\n但因為我地第一隊戰鬥人員 解散資料未del 出唔到閘 二妹(<span style=\"color: gold;\">趙慧妍</span>)出左閘 見我同大妹(<span style=\"color: gold;\">康美娜</span>)入唔到 兩個妹都喊曬口 最後都係分開左 二妹(<span style=\"color: gold;\">趙慧妍</span>) 先去戰場。<br />\n<br />\n我同大妹(<span style=\"color: gold;\">康美娜</span>) 最後係坐香港地鐵返家<br />\n<br />\n轉個撚頭 去撚左場 電音show 見到我fd 之後唔知同佢講咩q野 坐低睇show 點知zedd(電音Dj) 講我隔離<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">利申:本人都喜歡edm</span><br />\n我又驚又開心 之後同佢講(英文):好欣賞佢我都有作曲 問佢啲技巧 最後話會去佢黎緊香港個 EDM show 之後光速完show(夢show) 離場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">ZEDD</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/14/185654_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F14%2F185654_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a4d2dd62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n訓醒<br />\n完"},{"pid":"9f248b7016062dea9a7aee645770d5f94f3686ef","tid":592121,"uid":121864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T11:16:30.000Z","msg":"揸法拉利飛車 之後抄左 <br />\n利申 窮撚"}]}